{
  "texts": [
    "Utilizing video conferencing platforms such as Google Meet and Zoom, these face-to-face interactions lasted approximately 30 min per session.",
    "We designed a comprehensive, closed-ended survey questionnaire for data collection purposes based on insights gleaned from the interviews and relevant variables identified in the 6G-SQC literature.",
    "This method was selected as it is a widely-accepted approach for efficiently acquiring information from a sizable and diverse population.",
    "The questionnaire was divided into two categories, with the first focusing on demographic questions and the second consisting of closed-ended questions based on project attributes.",
    "We employed a 9-point rating scale, ranging from extremely low (EL) to extremely high (EH), to evaluate the participant's responses."
  ]
}